{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja template for Spectra LS Phase 3 Slice-02 selection-handoff one-shot validation. #}
{# Version: 2026.04.19.4 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-04-19 #}

{# =========================
  Phase 3-S02 Selection-Handoff Validation (custom_components/spectra_ls)
  Purpose: validate selection-handoff readiness diagnostics emitted by one-shot sequence.
  Workflow:
    1) Run: spectra_ls.run_p3_s02_sequence
    2) Reload this template and inspect selection_handoff_validation + write_controls
  ========================= #}

{% set freshness_required_s = 180 %}
{% set s_target = 'sensor.shadow_active_target' if states['sensor.shadow_active_target'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target' %}
{% set s_path = 'sensor.shadow_active_control_path' if states['sensor.shadow_active_control_path'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_path' %}

{% set active_target = states(s_target) %}
{% set active_path = states(s_path) %}
{% set route_trace = state_attr(s_target,'route_trace') or {} %}
{% set route_decision = route_trace.decision if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.decision is defined else '' %}
{% set route_reason = route_trace.reason if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.reason is defined else '' %}

{% set contract_validation = state_attr(s_target,'contract_validation') or {} %}
{% set contract_ready = contract_validation is mapping and contract_validation.valid is defined %}
{% set contract_valid = contract_validation.valid if contract_ready else false %}

{% set write_controls = state_attr(s_target,'write_controls') or {} %}
{% set authority_mode = write_controls.authority_mode if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.authority_mode is defined else '' %}
{% set last_attempt = write_controls.last_attempt if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.last_attempt is defined and write_controls.last_attempt is mapping else {} %}
{% set last_status = last_attempt.status if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.status is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set last_reason = last_attempt.reason if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.reason is defined else '' %}

{% set handoff = state_attr(s_target,'selection_handoff_validation') or {} %}
{% set handoff_ready = handoff is mapping and handoff.ready_for_handoff is defined %}
{% set handoff_verdict = handoff.verdict if handoff is mapping and handoff.verdict is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set helper = handoff.helper if handoff is mapping and handoff.helper is defined and handoff.helper is mapping else {} %}
{% set helper_exists = helper.exists if helper is mapping and helper.exists is defined else false %}
{% set helper_options_count = helper.options_count if helper is mapping and helper.options_count is defined else 0 %}
{% set helper_target_in_options = helper.target_in_options if helper is mapping and helper.target_in_options is defined else false %}

{% set compat = handoff.compatibility if handoff is mapping and handoff.compatibility is defined and handoff.compatibility is mapping else {} %}
{% set missing_scripts = compat.missing_scripts if compat is mapping and compat.missing_scripts is defined else [] %}
{% set missing_automation_ids = compat.missing_automation_ids if compat is mapping and compat.missing_automation_ids is defined else [] %}

{% set captured_at = state_attr(s_target,'captured_at') | default('', true) %}
{% set captured_ts = as_timestamp(captured_at) if captured_at not in ['', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'none', none] else none %}
{% set captured_age_s = (as_timestamp(now()) - captured_ts) if captured_ts is not none else none %}
{% set snapshot_fresh = captured_age_s is not none and captured_age_s <= freshness_required_s %}

{% set route_ok = route_decision == 'route_linkplay_tcp' %}

{% set verdict = 'FAIL' %}
{% if handoff_verdict == 'PASS' and handoff_ready and route_ok and contract_valid and helper_exists and helper_target_in_options and snapshot_fresh and (missing_scripts | length) == 0 and (missing_automation_ids | length) == 0 %}
  {% set verdict = 'PASS' %}
{% elif handoff_verdict in ['PASS','WARN'] and route_ok and snapshot_fresh and (contract_valid or not contract_ready) %}
  {% set verdict = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}

### Phase 3-S02 Selection-Handoff Validation (`spectra_ls`)
- Result: **{{ verdict }}**
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**

### Routing + authority context
- Active target (`{{ s_target }}`): **{{ active_target }}**
- Active path (`{{ s_path }}`): **{{ active_path }}**
- Route decision/reason: **{{ route_decision if route_decision != '' else 'n/a' }}** / **{{ route_reason if route_reason != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- Authority mode: **{{ authority_mode if authority_mode != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- Contract ready/valid: **{{ contract_ready }} / {{ contract_valid }}**
- Snapshot fresh (<= {{ freshness_required_s }}s): **{{ snapshot_fresh }}** (age={{ (captured_age_s | round(1)) if captured_age_s is not none else 'n/a' }}s)

### Selection handoff diagnostics
- Handoff payload ready: **{{ handoff_ready }}**
- Handoff verdict: **{{ handoff_verdict }}**
- Helper exists: **{{ helper_exists }}**
- Helper options count: **{{ helper_options_count }}**
- Active target in helper options: **{{ helper_target_in_options }}**
- Missing scripts: **{{ missing_scripts | length }}**
- Missing automation ids: **{{ missing_automation_ids | length }}**

### Last write attempt (if write trial enabled)
- Status: **{{ last_status }}**
- Reason: **{{ last_reason if last_reason != '' else 'n/a' }}**

### Guidance
{% if verdict == 'PASS' %}
- Selection-handoff readiness is healthy for guarded P3-S02 progression.
{% elif verdict == 'WARN' %}
- Core diagnostics are present but compatibility/readiness is incomplete.
- Re-run `spectra_ls.run_p3_s02_sequence`; if warnings persist, review missing scripts/automation IDs and helper options.
{% else %}
- Missing/invalid S02 diagnostics context. Confirm the integration is loaded and rerun `spectra_ls.run_p3_s02_sequence`.
{% endif %}
